creator: MyCarSpot
descriptionHtml:
Many companies are providing car park spaces to some of their employees depending on various criteria like hierarchy or distance from home. But the employees are sometimes away from the office, traveling, working from home, on sick leave or even using their motorbike when it's sunny. The car park space is left empty while other people could have used it! So why don't you start sharing the empty spaces automatically?

MyCarSpot is an online service to simplify company car park user's life and to make happy employees by sharing empty car park spaces.

The service is free for parking with up to 5 car spaces.
descriptionShort: MyCarSpot optimises your company car park and co-workers mobility.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Support for the registration of new users with administrator approval workflow.

title: MyCarSpot

creator: MyCarSpot
descriptionHtml:
Some employees have assigned parking spaces or workstation, but do not use them every day because of work from home, travel, holidays ... MyCarSpot allows those who do not have one to reserve these available spaces directly via the application. The company does not have to do anything, MyCarSpot takes care of the places allocation!

And to manage the flow of people at the cafeteria at lunchtime and thus respect the rules of distance and space filling, employees can reserve a slot among those that are not full.


The service is free for parking with up to 5 car spaces.
descriptionShort: MyCarSpot manages corporate shared spaces: car park, workstations and cafeteria.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Support for the new user interface. Fixing a crash at startup.

title: MyCarSpot

creator: Sharvy
descriptionHtml:
Sharvy is a digital solution to manage corporate shared resources. All in one application, optimize your parking spaces, workstations and/or cafeteria.

The goal: Making it easier for employees to reserve spots and favor mobility. In the current context of a health crisis, Sharvy allows you to watch the attendance rate of your offices/workplaces and also ensure that the health of your workers isn’t being put at risk.

Key features:
• Release and reservation of parking spaces and workstations by employees,
• Reservation of a slot in the cafeteria,
• Automatic allocation of spaces by our algorithm, according to the priority rules defined by the administrator and according to his work team,
• Management of the type of parking spaces (small vehicle, SUV, bike, motorbike, electric vehicle, PRM, carpooling, etc.), areas and workstations,
• Definition of the occupancy rate,
• Dynamic map of the car park and workstations,
• Access control to the car park by camera with plate recognition or mobile app,
• Management of days off and connection to your HRIS,
• Occupancy and usage statistics for the app.

Take advantage of our free offer and test the solution on 5 parking spaces, 5 workstations and 2 canteen spaces.
descriptionShort: Digital solution to manage corporate shared resources

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Bug fixes.

descriptionHtml:
Sharvy is a digital solution to manage corporate shared resources. All in one application, optimize your parking spaces, workstations and/or cafeteria.

The goal: Making it easier for employees to reserve spots and favor mobility. In the current context of a health crisis, Sharvy allows you to watch the attendance rate of your offices/workplaces and also ensure that the health of your workers isn’t being put at risk.

Key features:
• Release and reservation of parking spaces and workstations by employees,
• Reservation of a slot in the cafeteria,
• Automatic allocation of spaces by our algorithm, according to the priority rules defined by the administrator and according to his work team,
• Management of the type of parking spaces (small vehicle, SUV, bike, motorbike, electric vehicle, PRM, carpooling, etc.), areas and workstations,
• Definition of the occupancy rate,
• Dynamic map of the car park and workstations,
• Access control to the car park by camera with plate recognition or mobile app,
• Management of days off and connection to your HRIS,
• Occupancy and usage statistics for the app.

Take advantage of our free offer and test the solution on 5 parking spaces, 5 workstations and 2 canteen spaces.
descriptionShort: Digital solution to manage corporate shared resources

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Compatibility with the new parking features (to be activated by the administrator):
- Lock the reservation when the user enters the car park.
- Automatic reservation cancellation if the user doesn't arrive on time (no-show).
